Posted: Sep 17 04 8:40 PM <br>
Second raid is spawned by reentering DN after giving Lantaric the blackened bones. It can be respawned at will by camping or zoning in and out of DN. Vesthan is back with some guards and you must kill him. this time he dies and spawnsa Dracolich of Hsagra. The draco from this fight drops the orb. read below for more details. <br>
<br>
Finished second raid. Had 53 GoD geared people and lived with 14 Left BUT thats because we had no clue what would happens and weren't prepared. You can trigger the encounter at will by just camping out and back in once it has poofed. <br>
<br>
I would say 30 GoD geared people ready for it could do it easily. The loot was a$ for the difficulty, 115Hp boots attuneable. Once again won't spoil whole fight especially since you cannot blow it. Just as a hint put clerics in all groups ( or at least shaman) and load up cure/word of replenishement <br>
<br>
